member.name: M:Orchid.E.Common.Print.PaperSize.PopulateItemsCore(System.String)
member.summary:
Reads the internal element to get all the family or instance parameters, and adds them to the Items collection.
Items are sorted alphabetically by name. If the SelectedIndex is already set, it is set to zero.
